No. 518. Bank of British Columbia, Petitioner, v. Percy P. Moore, Administrator, etc. January 25, 1904. Mr. John F. Dillon, Mr. Harry Hubbard, Mr. John M. Dillon, Mr. Fisher A. *607Baker añd Mr. Sidney T. Smith for petitioner. Mr. Charles S. Wheeler for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
